{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 3129749, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "工物吧，有挺多好方向的（别定向都好说", "timestamp": 1638886548, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3129761, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从方便转的角度看，工物", "timestamp": 1638886618, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3129772, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建筑比较适合肯吃苦有兴趣有天赋的，这三个里起码占一个……如果对建筑不是很了解建议工物", "timestamp": 1638886752, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3129799, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "😂工物课程会难不少……", "timestamp": 1638886998, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3129803, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有兴趣学的话应该还好", "timestamp": 1638887032, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3129822, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "妥妥工物啊 虽然没有互联网金融这么热 但是铁饭碗啊 和军工搭上边 有啥犹豫的", "timestamp": 1638887231, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3129848, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建筑转前端好转", "timestamp": 1638887483, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3130178, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建筑需要先测眼睛，入学会考画画+学制是5年，可能是建筑的很大的demerit", "timestamp": 1638890417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3130716, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建筑≥工物非定向＞＞＞＞工物定向", "timestamp": 1638894194, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3132236, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "工物非定向，方向多以后也方便转。", "timestamp": 1638931768, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3137368, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 592481, "reply_to": 3130178, "tag": null, "text": "建筑适合躺平混毕业，但前提是心理比较强大，对自己要求不高，比较喜欢设计（至少不是很排斥）。理论上建筑只要交图就不会挂科，期末考试也几乎没有。毕业后就业的话，可以做其他类型的设计，也可以进地产行业。建院也有参数化设计之类跟cs交叉的方向，有大佬学长申了cmu的cs phd。工物可能有些数理课程会比较难，不能太混子，转码比建筑简单。我觉得选哪个主要看个人兴趣，如果对艺术和设计一点兴趣都没有，那还是去工物吧。", "timestamp": 1639020828, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 592481, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "替一个不懂专业知识的学弟问一下，虽然我知道都是坑，如果在矬子里边拔将军，工程物理跟建筑更推荐哪个(如果有可比性的话？问了建筑的同学，有说建筑真tm坑的，有说建筑还行的；也问了工物的同学，有说工物有好方向的，有说快跑的，dz有点糊涂了", "timestamp": 1638886355, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1639020828, "url": "", "vote": {}}}